    <p>HELP FOR WORK­ERS</p>
    <p>Jobs Sup­port Scheme ex­tended till March Up to 50% wage sup­port for hard-hit sec­tors.</p>
    <p>$1b Jobs Growth In­cen­tive</p>
    <p>• Wage sub­sidy for firms such as those in growth sec­tors to hire lo­cals.</p>
    <p>• Up to 25% for work­ers be­low 40; up to 50% for work­ers 40 and over.</p>
    <p>Covid-19 Sup­port Grant, Work­fare Spe­cial Payment ex­tended SUP­PORT­ING AVI­A­TION, TOURISM</p>
    <p>$187m to ex­tend avi­a­tion sup­port to March In­cludes cost re­lief for air­lines, ground han­dlers, air­port ten­ants. $320m in vouch­ers to spur lo­cal tourism</p>
    <p>TRANS­FORM­ING THE ECON­OMY</p>
    <p>Up to $150m to en­hance Startup SG Founder pro­gramme in phases Start-up cap­i­tal grant to be raised, men­tor­ship to con­tinue.</p>

